    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Set of Quantity Values being attributed to a measurand together with any other available relevant information</skos:definition>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Measurement Result</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A measurement result generally contains “relevant information” about the set of quantity values, such that some may be more representative of the measurand than others. This may be expressed in the form of a probability density function (PDF).</skos:scopeNote>
